{"tid":494731,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我阿爸又響屋企大大聲咁睇支那片","createTime":"2017-12-10T03:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T04:26:02.000Z","uid":103325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"257698b570fb1e8629e16c525bfc94fd103dc795","tid":494731,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:32:18.000Z","msg":"真係好後悔教佢用 smart phone<br />\n佢成日開住個電話大大聲咁睇片都算，但佢睇嘅係支那片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本身好怕嘈，亦好撚憎支那話，一聽到就會好撚燥，我戴耳塞佢地又話我好戴耳塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaacff1ab7a729a0164357231fe728736cbf9bbd","tid":494731,"uid":142253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:33:24.000Z","msg":"用電視/電腦大大聲播反共片"},{"pid":"6f9f341e5a24e3bd266e00ffeba16f1e4c9f852c","tid":494731,"uid":71725,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:37:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"686e777d2276fe951941b0770c758368cc6dc09b","tid":494731,"uid":74380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"咁咪叫佢用headphone"},{"pid":"17fdd089af851fa629ec8c19b0aec32fb4d7650d","tid":494731,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:05:28.000Z","msg":"原來就係你呢d 人<br />\n搞到通街老野睇片唔熄聲又唔戴headphone <br />\n仲要支那片"},{"pid":"292221f3271f9adf6e533d901c2b537002eb9add","tid":494731,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"其實之前我都有叫過佢用 headphone，有一次響醫院，佢陪我去做檢查，等緊個陣佢響度睇片，唔係好大聲，我話俾個 headphones 佢用，佢竟然答我：呢度個電視都有聲架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最衰係我，平時無乜理佢，搞到佢羣埋班廢老，而家仲誤入歧途變埋支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}